J. H. ROSSBACH & BRO. v. UNITED STATES. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. April 18, 1903.) No. 104. Appeal from the Circuit Court of the United States for the • Southern District of New York. For opinion below, see 116 Fed. 781. W. W. Smith, for appellant. Chas. I. Baker, for the United States.

Before TOWNSEND and COXE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Affirmed in open court
